Aura of Glory			KEY:Insinuator ~ Aura of Glory			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Antipaladin Class Feature.InsinuatorClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Supernatural.Aura																		SOURCEPAGE:p.21		DESC:An insinuator can expend two uses of his smite impudence ability to grant the ability to smite impudence to all allies within 10 feet, using his bonuses. Allies must use this smite impudence ability before the start of the insinuator’s next turn, and the bonuses last for 1 minute. Using this ability is a free action.
Aura of Belief			KEY:Insinuator ~ Aura of Belief			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Antipaladin Class Feature.InsinuatorClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Supernatural.Aura																		SOURCEPAGE:p.21		DESC:An insinuator’s weapons are treated as chaos-aligned while he invokes a chaotic outsider, law-aligned when he invokes a lawful outsider, or evil-aligned while he invokes an evil outsider. If he invokes an outsider with more than one alignment aura, the insinuator must choose during the initial invocation which alignment his weapon radiates.
